hir]] {{spaced ndash}} British businesswoman, founder and CEO of Peek.com, travel company based in San Francisco, California<ref name=\"USA Today\">{{cite news|last=Graham|first=Jefferson|title=Start-up travel site offers a Peek at hidden gems|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/columnist/talkingtech/2012/12/20/peek-offers-travel-advice-and-tips/1782251/|accessdate=24 January 2013|newspaper=USA Today|date=20 December 2012}}</ref>\n* [[Shelim Hussain]] [[Order of the British Empire|MBE]] {{spaced ndash}} entrepreneur, founder and managing director ofEuro Foods (UK) Limited<ref name=\"redhotcurry\">{{cite news|url=http://www.redhotcurry.com/food_and_drink/other/shelim_hussain.htm|title=Food Entrepreneur Wins AOC Gold Award|date=5 June 2005|accessdate=6 January 2008|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207172850/http://www.redhotcurry.com/food_and_drink/other/shelim_hussain.htm|archivedate=7 February 2008|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* [[Siraj Ali]] {{spaced ndash}} restaurateur and philanthropist;<ref name=\"echo\">{{cite news |last=McNally|first=Alex|url=http://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/4315631.Restaurant_boss_Siraj_praised_for_community_dedication/|title=Restaurant boss Siraj praised for community dedication|location=Essex|work= |publisher=Echo|date=25 April 2009|accessdate=1 January 2013}}</ref> recipient of the 2011 British Bangladeshi Who's Who \"Outstanding Contribution\" Award<ref name=\"menmedia\">{{cite news |last= |first= |url=http://menmedia.co.uk/asiannews/news/s/1462249_bangladeshi-restaurant-entrepreneur-honoured|title=Bangladeshi restaurant entrepreneur honoured|location=Manchester|work= [[Manchester Evening News]]|date=19 October 2011|accessdate=1 July 2013}}</ref>\n* [[Sultan Choudhury]] {{spaced ndash}} businessman; managing director of the [[Islamic Bank of Britain]]<ref name=\"newhorizon\">{{cite news|url=http://www.newhorizon-islamicbanking.com/index.cfm?section=features&action=view&id=11412|title=An Interview with Sultan Choudhur